snippet.title: Triangle/cross // BL Game - Official trailer!
snippet.description:
Triangle/cross last official trailer is out!
💛💙🧡

Our new BL game Triangle/cross has been released! 🎉

Take a look at the last official trailer! ✨

Are you ready for this game where two love triangles intersect? 💖

Download the game here:
✨ Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=info.otomedou.fwe.trianglecEn

✨ App Store: 
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bl-triangle-cross/id1472482085?l=ja&ls=1
